videos.description: West Virginia guard Miles McBride comes up with a steal, flies toward the rim and kicks it to Derek Culver, who rocks the rim with a jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (McBride's steal leads to Culver's dunk for WVU) 2020/02/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: McBride's steal leads to Culver's dunk for WVU

videos.description: TCU guard Desmond Bane appears to drop in the go-ahead layup with 0.9 seconds left, but the basket doesn't count as he is called for an offensive foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Bane's go-ahead layup negated by offensive foul call) 2020/02/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bane's go-ahead layup negated by offensive foul call

videos.description: TCU guard Jaire Grayer lobs the ball underneath to center Kevin Samuel, who then drops in a layup to extend the Horned Frogs' lead late in overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Grayer feeds Samuel late for clutch TCU bucket) 2020/02/22 ESHEET

videos.headline: Grayer feeds Samuel late for clutch TCU bucket
